- Create an image tag cloud so that images can be constrained by
  multiple tags.
- Migrate from SHA1 hashes of entire image files to version 5 UUIDs to
  identify images.
- Write code for hashing just the image pixels while ignoring all the
  other contents of the image file.
- Create some method for uploading multiple images and checking for
  duplicate images.
- Implement logging code.
- Make it possible to change the datetime on the image.
- Make it possible to rotate the image.
- Provide a way of getting back from an img-view of an image back to
  the set of photos that the user was originally looking at.
- Refactor the code.
- Clean up the code.
- Add support for users and groups.
- Make the code reusable (i.e. build a higher-level language).
